column5: Well guys and gals fishing has been awesome this past week off St Catharines ...Wire Dipsys back 155 on a 2 setting spin doctors and flies and riggers down 155 to 185 useing echips and meat get out and enjoy what Lake Ontario has to offer. Ps : Tune into Giant Fm 91.7 Classic Rock over the next few weeks for a chance to Win a fishing charter with me
Im seeing some huge steelhead in the mix!  Nice work
Nice work Steve !!!! Some very happy fishermen with some very nice mix of Lake Ontario salmon & steel !!!!! Well done......
